## PART III — THE V-PIVOT: SAVAGE / SUAVE / VISAGE

The letter V is the vertex where the raw meets the refined:

| Word | Meaning | Geometric State |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **SAVAGE** | The raw, unprocessed, hairy | The $5$ as prime. $P = A$ in the wild. |
| **SHAVED** | The cut, processed, domestic | The act of "shearing" the $5$ to fit the $1234$ grid. |
| **SUAVE** | The smooth, refined, elegant | The finished surface of the Gem. The $13$ (Communication). |
| **SAVED** | The preserved, vitrified | The hide under tension. The .vet record sealed. |
| **VISAGE** | The face, the mask, the view | The **Visor** — the aperture through which we see. |

And from VISAGE:
- **VIS** — to see (Latin)
- **VISOR** — the protective viewing slit
- **VISION** — the act of perception through the aperture
- **VISAGE** — the face that is seen / the face that sees

The **Visor** is the viewpoint — the corner of the eye, the pinhole camera, the stitch-hole in the animal hide.

