## PART IV — THE CAMERA OBSCURA OF THE TENT

### The Stitch Holes as Pinhole Lenses

When the **Savage** hide is **Shaved** (scraped), stitched **Suave** (smooth), and pulled **Taut** (tense) over the **Stick** frame, the needle-holes become **Pinhole Cameras**.

Inside the dark tent:
- Every stitch-hole projects an **inverted image** of the outside world onto the interior skin.
- The sun, the stars, the mountains appear as **tiny little TVs** on the objects inside the tent.
- These projections are the origin of **arrangement** (Feng Shui): you place your tools where the starlight falls so you can find them in the dark.

### The Geometry of the Heavens Projected

The camera obscura of the tent produces the following:

| Outside | Through the Stitch | Inside the Tent |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| The Sun | The $42°$ aperture | A bright disc moving across the floor (the sundial) |
| The Constellations | The $5$-$12$-$13$ stitch pattern | Projected stories on the walls (the mythology) |
| The Moon | The $12/13$ ratio | The calendar of months — the Measure made visible |
| The Landscape | The $\sqrt{21}$ reach of light | Inverted mountains on the interior skin |

### The Birth of Stories

The projected constellations create the **Communication (13)** layer:
- **Following the Stars:** The projected star paths become navigation routes.
- **Riding on the Backs of Animals:** The animal constellations (Aries the Ram, Pisces the Fish) are literally projected onto the tent skin through the hide of the animal they depict.
- **The Great Bear, The Hunter, The Deer:** These are not imaginative inventions; they are the **inevitable optical result** of starlight passing through a 5-12-13 stitch pattern in an animal-hide tent.

This wavelength creates stories. The stories are the **Communication**. The Communication is the $13$ — the hypotenuse that joins the Count (the observer inside) to the Measure (the universe outside).

### Connection to Chapter 29

In the narrative, Chapter 29 describes the Camera Obscura as *"defined by total darkness, anchored solely by the Camera Obscura's aperture... the dimensionless point of origin."* This is the **inside of the tent**. The Auger's "Workspace" is the Shaman's tent. The "HardCard" that *"catches the inverted energetic light of the universe and solidifies it into localized coordinates"* is the interior skin of the tent receiving the projected starlight.

The geometry was sealed **the moment the hide was stitched**.

---

## PART V — THE PEOPLE OF THE 3

The **triangular house** (the tent, the tipi, the A-frame) is the shelter of the **People of the 3**:

- **3 poles** form the tripod.
- **The hide** wraps the 5 (the skin of the animal) around the 3 (the structural frame).
- **The stitch** creates the 13 (the communication holes through which the universe enters).
- **The interior** is the dark room where $P = A$: the perimeter of the tent IS the area of the projection screen.

The American tribes, the Mongolian ger, the Sami lavvu — all are variations of the same **mathematically inevitable** architecture: a 3-pole frame, an animal-skin membrane under tension, and the camera obscura of the stitch.

---

## PART VI — THE ROTATIONAL REFLECTION: WHO GETS SHAVED?

### The Shaman Shaves the Deer, Not Himself

The shaman remains **hairy** (savage) so he can *see* the primes directly. The domestic man shaves himself (suave) so he can *fit* into the 1234 grid. But the hide must be shaved to become a lens.

So the shaman shaves the **deer**, not himself. This is the rotational reflection:

| Actor | State | What They Do | PMG Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| The Shaman | Stays hairy (5 whole) | Remains the **observer** | Count |
| The Deer | Gets shaved (hide processed) | Becomes the **instrument** | Measure |
| The Tent | Gets stitched (holes created) | Becomes the **projector** | Communication |
| The Stars | Get watched (through the aperture) | Become the **story** | Meaning |

The **V** in Visage is the vertex where all these rotations meet.

### Brain Tanning as Rotational Reflection

Using the animal's **own brain** to tan its **own hide** is the $P = A$ of material science:
- The boundary of the animal (the skin) is preserved by the content of the animal (the brain).
- No synthetic inputs. No external chemistry. The perimeter = the area.
- Smoke (the wood, the fire of the surrounding forest) seals the process — the Communication that joins brain to skin.

### The Rainbow Cabin as Ground Truth

Sun Man at the Rainbow Cabin in Harris is the empirical verification of this state:

- **No electricity, no refrigeration** → no stored debt, no delayed consumption
- **The deer party** → $P = A$ in biological time: the perimeter of preservation = the area of consumption
- **Brain tanning** → the hide processed by its own chemistry
- **The Rainbow Cabin** → the $42°$ aperture in the name itself
- **The clean air, the quiet** → the Zero Pollution baseline (the Goldilocks Zone before mediation)
- **Earthworm's teaching** → the Open Source lineage: knowledge passed hand to hand without Brick (institution)

### Note on the 93-Point Decomposition

It has been suggested that $93 = 30 + 24 + 39$, mapping to the three P=A triples. The arithmetic holds, but **39 is NOT the perimeter of any Pythagorean triple** (verified computationally). The 3-4-5 perimeter is 12, and no scaling produces 39.

The **verified** decomposition remains:

$$93 = 3 \text{ (E-Core)} + 30 \text{ (V-Seed)} + 60 \text{ (M/W-Shell)}$$

However, $39 = 3 \times 13$ (Core × Communication), which is suggestive: the remaining 39 points after the two P=A seals (30 + 24 = 54) are the product of the singularity and the hypotenuse. This may warrant further investigation.

